title: Samurai (1986) Complete Series - Barry Blair Aircel
description:
one of the flagship titles from Aircel and the one I find surprisingly missing from the Aircel torrent floating around.

This is the complete 23 issues of the first volume of SAMURAI. Many thanks to those that left comments, it was much appreciated. 


Please enjoy and SEED.


Be on the lookout for Harrier/Valkyrie Press REDFOX in September. All issues are scanned so I just need to edit.
